id: pm-5baq
title: Verify and repair pm-changelog-generated main CHANGELOG release alignment
description: "Reinstall latest pm-changelog, verify main CHANGELOG.md generation against current released pm-cli version and release workflow, ensure clickable pm item references and SDK/package support are functional, and file upstream pm-changelog issues for package-side defects instead of patching them locally."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: changelog,ci,packages,release,sdk
created_at: "2026-05-24T13:53:07.492Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T14:49:06.738Z"
author: codex-changelog-verify
parent: pm-59gj
resolution: completed
expected_result: "pm-cli uses latest pm-changelog to generate CHANGELOG.md for the actual released version range, with SDK package contracts and CI/release checks proving the flow."
actual_result: "Installed pm-changelog 2026.5.24-11, generated CHANGELOG.md for v2026.5.24 with 39 closed items, fixed release-note evidence bounds, verified package doctor/contracts, full release gate, live Sentry/telemetry, and linked pm tests."
comments[7]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T13:55:31.728Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Issue found: pm-changelog@2026.5.24-9 can pass --check while grouping most closed tracker history under ## Unreleased because pm-cli's package-owned check script uses --group-by release without a release version/range. Filed upstream unbraind/pm-changelog#8 for a package-owned release mode instead of adding a custom generator in pm-cli."
  "2026-05-24T14:07:21.578Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Verification note: focused release-readiness test initially failed because it still required ## Unreleased in CHANGELOG.md. Updated the marker to the package-generated 2026.5.24 release heading."
  "2026-05-24T14:24:13.529Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Verification note: npm latest pm-changelog is 2026.5.24-11, installed project extension is 2026.5.24-11, changelog generate help/contracts expose release tag range flags, and pnpm changelog:pm:check passes against CHANGELOG.md with item_count=39 and clickable pm item URLs for v2026.5.24."
  "2026-05-24T14:30:46.949Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Issue found and fixed in pm-cli release-note helper: retrospective notes for an existing release tag could include post-tag pm tracker updates in the PM Tracker Evidence footer. The changelog remains package-owned; the helper now bounds tracker evidence by the release tag timestamp when the tag exists."
  "2026-05-24T14:40:54.119Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Evidence: full live release gate passed with build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, 100% coverage (108 files/1622 tests), version policy, secret scan, npx smoke, package-first dogfood, npm pack, compatibility check, and required Sentry/telemetry. Sentry unbrained/pm-cli returned 0 critical / 4 high / 4 total relevant unresolved issues under threshold; telemetry required mode returned finish_error_rate_pct=2.74 and failures_without_error_code_rows=0. Telemetry stack health showed API ok version 2026.5.24, queue pm.telemetry.events depth 0 with 1 consumer, and 19,635 events in the last 24h; recent events were live at 2026-05-24 16:36 Europe/Vienna."
  "2026-05-24T14:48:15.330Z",codex-changelog-verify,"CI follow-up: GitHub static gate failed because PR checkouts were shallow, so pm-changelog could not resolve previous/current release tags for --since-previous-tag/--until-release-tag. Updated CI checkouts to fetch full history/tags for tag-aware changelog checks and added contract coverage."
  "2026-05-24T14:49:06.738Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Verification after CI checkout fix: release-automation contract test passed (10 tests), pnpm changelog:pm:check passed with changed=false and item_count=39, and pnpm quality:static passed locally."
